title: Episode 72: Ft G Herbo
itunes:title: Episode 72: Ft G Herbo
description:
Chiraqs GHerbo stops by and has some belated Birthday shots with Angela Yee, Stephanie Santiago & Gigi Maguire. He discusses finally being legal. The ladies grill him on his body count, his first time going down on a female and how good he was, who he's bringing home for the holidays and even tells the ladies a funny story about his inches compared to his dads.
